text: Might as well post another video, it should be good enough to give you an idea of his style and see if you want to discover more of his work. Luv(sic) is a series of 6 songs about "love, parting and uniting". Nujabes died after Part 3, so Shing02 decided to take his beats and finish the project. Parts 4 to 6 really take a double meaning, you can clearly see that Shing02 wrote part of the lyrics for his departed friend (Part 5's lyrics start with "'till death do us apart, and it did"). Great hexalogy.
